      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/futures-tread-higher-ahead-latest-inflation-test-2024-04-10/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[好於預期的通膨數據給聯準會最早於 6 月開始降息的希望潑了一盆冷水，週三美國股市收盤下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/futures-tread-higher-ahead-latest-inflation-test-2024-04-10/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 10:17:54 GMT</pubDate>
